# Input

```svelte
<Component
/* block comment */
prop="value"
/>
<Component
// line comment
prop="value"
/>
<Component /* inline block comment */ prop="value" />
<Component // inline line comment
prop="value" />
<Component.Member
/* block comment */
prop="value"
/>

```


# Formatted

```svelte
<Component
	/* block comment */
	prop="value"
/>
<Component
	// line comment
	prop="value"
/>
<Component /* inline block comment */ prop="value" />
<Component
	// inline line comment
	prop="value"
/>
<Component.Member
	/* block comment */
	prop="value"
/>

```
